        {
            "title": "聯準會洛根表示央行應避免釋出降息傾向訊號",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8uWFVPeORr9rf4z5xkDehA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/Brazil-Stock-Market_3_M_1440048532.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 達拉斯聯邦儲備銀行總裁洛麗·洛根(Lorie Logan)週五表示,鑑於經濟前景的不確定性和持續的通膨擔憂,央行不應釋出下一步政策行動將是降息的訊號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根解釋了她本週在聯邦公開市場委員會(FOMC)會議聲明中投下反對票的原因,稱鑑於當前貨幣政策面臨的雙向風險,聯準會不應提供暗示偏好降息的前瞻性指引。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">她與另外兩位地區聯儲銀行總裁一同投票反對暗示聯準會下一步行動將是降息的措辭。洛根支持聯準會將利率目標維持在3.5%至3.75%之間的決定。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-bbb07824-19fe-392e-974e-442335cbfcdc-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根表示,在通膨回歸2%目標的持續擔憂下,經濟前景高度不確定。鑑於當前展望,FOMC的下一次利率變動可能是升息或降息,她說。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根表示,她對將通膨率降回2%越來越感到擔憂,同時指出就業市場一直保持穩定。她補充說,通膨路徑的前景仍不確定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">洛根表示,當FOMC提供前瞻性指引時,該指引必須反映政策展望,這一點非常重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E6%BA%96%E6%9C%83%E6%B4%9B%E6%A0%B9%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E6%87%89%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E9%87%8B%E5%87%BA%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E5%82%BE%E5%90%91%E8%A8%8A%E8%99%9F-150608585.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 23:30:47",
