        },
        {
            "title": "為何布蘭特原油價格未大幅飆升?Yardeni發表看法",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/wwIi1eNosr5D3CRzCCFOrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_2_M_1440048332.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 自2月28日起荷莫茲海峽關閉,這是石油市場歷史上最大規模的供應中斷,導致全球供應減少逾15%,然而布蘭特原油僅小幅上漲至90美元至100美元區間。Yardeni Research對此作出解釋。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構指出六大因素緩和了許多分析師原本預期的更嚴重價格飆升,部分預測曾預計油價將達到每桶150美元至200美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首先,替代基礎設施發揮了作用。沙烏地阿拉伯和阿聯酋提升了管道運輸能力,合計每日輸送約700萬桶石油,而此前通過海峽運輸的石油量為每日1700萬至2000萬桶。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dffe5d96-0720-3742-a9a6-c46c2affffb3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其次,來自伊朗和俄羅斯石油豁免的緊急供應、國際能源署戰略儲備釋放以及中國庫存轉售進一步緩衝了市場。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第三,Yardeni表示全球價格只是故事的一半。\"雖然基準布蘭特原油價格維持在每桶100美元附近,但這並不代表全球油價的真實情況,\"該機構寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"運抵亞洲的杜拜原油價格曾飆升至每桶260美元。整個亞洲的當地買家正支付溢價。\"</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">接下來,Yardeni指出需求破壞正在加速,國際能源署目前預測2026年全球石油需求將收縮8萬桶/日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">第五,全球經濟的能源密集度據稱遠低於1970年代石油危機時期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">最後,石油期貨呈現陡峭的現貨溢價結構,顯示市場預期這是暫時性而非永久性的供應中斷。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">\"我們預計今年剩餘時間布蘭特原油將在每桶85美元至100美元區間交易,高於衝突前水平,\"Yardeni寫道。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該機構補充表示,只要長期通膨預期保持穩定,且工資-價格螺旋上升的風險維持在低水平,升息就不在考慮範圍內。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%82%BA%E4%BD%95%E5%B8%83%E8%98%AD%E7%89%B9%E5%8E%9F%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E6%A0%BC%E6%9C%AA%E5%A4%A7%E5%B9%85%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-yardeni%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%A8%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95-155634321.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-02 00:37:53",
