            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "特斯拉歐洲銷量持續回升,燃料成本上漲推動電動車需求",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/weOb9x2EBbh8ZF9DpmLg7Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC340AO_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特斯拉\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特斯拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特斯拉\">特斯拉</a>在歐洲部分市場的註冊量於4月份持續復甦,隨著伊朗戰爭後燃料價格飆升,丹麥、法國和荷蘭的銷量均有所增長,推動消費者對電動車的興趣。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span>特斯拉</span></span></span></span>在丹麥的4月份註冊量按年增長102%,根據bilstatistik.dk的數據顯示;而法國的註冊量則增長112%,根據PFA的數據。在荷蘭,汽車行業協會BOVAG報告稱,註冊量從去年的381輛增加23%至469輛。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">荷蘭的數據公布不久前,該國車輛管理局RDW於4月10日對特斯拉的全自動駕駛輔助軟件發出臨時批准。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d8c6bb43-86e2-383f-9c8a-fbe52be4768c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">RDW此後已通知歐盟委員會,表示有意為該軟件尋求歐盟範圍內的批准,特斯拉通過月度訂閱方式提供該軟件。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4月份的數據為特斯拉在歐洲的強勁開局增添了動力,第一季度該公司在整個歐洲大陸的註冊量增長近45%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次回升是在連續兩年銷量下滑之後出現的,包括2025年下降近27%。自2月28日伊朗戰爭開始以來,電動車的興趣加速增長,推動該地區燃料價格走高。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管出現復甦,競爭壓力正在加劇。在丹麥,特斯拉4月份的銷量少於中國電動車初創企業小鵬汽車,而在荷蘭則被比亞迪超越。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E9%8A%B7%E9%87%8F%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E5%9B%9E%E5%8D%87-%E7%87%83%E6%96%99%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%BB%8A%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82-134716820.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-01 22:20:42",
