        {
            "title": "多倫多證交所開盤走低 能源板塊波動持續",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/443mFuR.RWyxq4v0qKCvcw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPECAG0T8_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 加拿大主要股指週五早盤小幅下跌,能源價格降溫和地緣政治緊張情緒抑制了前一交易日大幅反彈的勢頭。截至美國東部時間09:40,S&amp;P/TSX綜合指數下跌61.12點,跌幅0.18%,報33,903.21點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一小幅回調是在週四強勁表現之後出現的,當時基準指數飆升1.94%,收於33,964.33點。藍籌股S&amp;P/TSX 60指數週五也略有回落,下跌0.21%至1,978.52點,此前在週四交易中上漲2.00%。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>華爾街受科技股強勢推動創新高</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市週五開盤創下歷史新高,延續了科技板塊強勁企業財報推動的漲勢。S&amp;P 500指數攀升0.4%,創下7,237.19點的新高峰,而納斯達克綜合指數突破25,000點大關,上漲0.5%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-82b67c25-5a61-3e14-8146-d17b0dbdd5dd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">蘋果公司(NASDAQ:AAPL)股價在早盤交易中跳漲逾4%,此前該公司提供了樂觀的營收指引和強勁的毛利率展望。Reddit Inc(NYSE:RDDT)也獲得顯著提振,飆升近10%,因其日活躍用戶增長超出華爾街預期。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>油價在伊朗緊張局勢中下滑</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原油價格繼續從四年高位回落,市場正在消化華盛頓與德黑蘭之間的升級威脅。布蘭特原油期貨下跌1.25%至109.02美元/桶,而WTI原油期貨下跌2.83%至102.10美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管價格下滑,但供應擔憂仍然高企,因為霍爾木茲海峽實際上已對全球運輸關閉。伊朗警告稱,如果總統唐納德·特朗普推進擬議的軍事選項,將對美國陣地發動「長期而痛苦的打擊」。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>黃金走弱 加息擔憂籠罩市場</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">黃金價格週五下滑,徘徊在一個月低點附近,投資者正在權衡持續通脹對央行政策的影響。XAU/USD價格下跌0.27%至4,617.24美元/盎司,延續了4月份金價下跌約1%的疲軟期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯準會和其他主要央行的鷹派信號最近對無收益資產造成壓力。政策制定者越來越多地對能源驅動的通脹發出警告,暗示利率可能需要在更長時間內保持較高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%9A%E5%80%AB%E5%A4%9A%E8%AD%89%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80%E9%96%8B%E7%9B%A4%E8%B5%B0%E4%BD%8E-%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E6%9D%BF%E5%A1%8A%E6%B3%A2%E5%8B%95%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C-145809531.html",
